<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.5">
<l>peṟṟāruñ cuṟṟamu meṉṟivai pēṇēṉnāṉ</l>
<l>maṟṟārum paṟṟilē ṉātalāl niṉṉaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>uṟṟāṉeṉ ṟuḷḷattu vaittaruḷ ceykaṇṭāy</l>
<l>kaṟṟārccēr kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I did not cherish these, calling [them] parents and relatives;</l>
<l>I had no attachment to anyone else, so I took refuge in you.</l>
<l>Look [here], saying, “He is my kinsman”</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] keeping [me] in [your] heart, grant me grace,</l>
<l>Lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram with learned men.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
